                  <history>
                  <origin>
                     <origDate notBefore="1400" notAfter="1499" evidence="lettering">15th century, possibly its first half.</origDate>
                     The manuscript once belonged to a monastery or a church from the region of <placeName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LOC5888Tana">Ṭānā</placeName>. 
                     In the concluding supplication on <locus target="#36vb"/>, the name of a commisioner 
                     <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS13991Alaryoan">Alarǝyoʾan</persName> is mentioned.
                     
